author: Timothy Puko
title: Analysts See 75 Billion-Cubic Feet Add to U.S. Natural-Gas Inventories
text:
Analysts expect government data scheduled for release Thursday to show natural-gas inventories this past week rose by about a fifth more than the five-year average for that time of the year.
